rows.label: tlk006101_05_msg0001
rows.name: There are a lot of good people in Avaritia.

rows.label: tlk006101_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I'd only been helping out at the port
until now, but Garram-san
told me the reason for it.

rows.label: tlk006101_05_msg0003
rows.name:
He said he had us do it so we could
get used to Avaritia and as training
to build our stamina and endurance.

rows.label: tlk006101_05_msg0004
rows.name:
We're going to do our best for the people here.
We have to properly repay the kindness we've received.
